  "slug": "sweet-almond-geranium-soap",
  "title": "Sweet almond and rose geranium soap",
  "subtitle": "A conditioning cold-process bar with sweet almond oil and rose geranium essential oil",
  "excerpt": "A cold-process bar soap with sweet almond oil replacing part of the olive fraction for a lighter, faster-lathering bar. Scented with rose geranium essential oil. The blend is 40% olive, 30% coconut, 20% sweet almond, 10% castor. Allow 4-6 weeks to harden before use.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "Susan Miller Cavitch, The Soapmaker's Companion (1997): carrier oil profiles and formulation balance. SoapCalc (accessed May 2026): sweet almond oil SAP value 0.136. USDA ACS oil database: sweet almond linoleic and oleic acid profile.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Sweet almond oil in cold-process soap acts much like olive oil. It traces a little faster. It gives a slightly lighter lather. It has a shorter shelf life thanks to its higher linoleic acid level. In this recipe it takes the place of part of the olive oil. The bar is milder than a coconut-heavy soap and softer than a pure bastille, with a clear floral scent from rose geranium essential oil.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Rose geranium (Pelargonium roseum) is a good essential oil for cold-process soap. It holds its scent well in the alkaline mix. Many citrus and floral oils fade badly through cure. Geranium keeps its character. The scent is soft and rosy-green, without the sweetness of a true rose absolute.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Wear protective gloves and goggles throughout the lye work. Add sodium hydroxide to water, not the reverse.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What you need",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ingredientsList",
        "attrs": {
          "items": [
            {
              "name": "Olive oil",
              "unit": "g",
